member.name: M:Tekla.Structures.Analysis.AnalysisPosition.Insert
member.summary: Inserts an analysis position. AnalysisModelName has to be set ID = Node ID Analysis object type has to be set: ANALYSIS_POSITION_BAR FatherObjectID = PartId FatherObject2ID = BarId ANALYSIS_POSITION_AREA FatherObjectID = PartId FatherObject2ID = AreaId ANALYSIS_POSITION_AREA_HOLE FatherObjectID = AreaId FatherObject2ID = HoleIndex (0..) ANALYSIS_POSITION_AREA_INNER FatherObjectID = PartId FatherObject2ID = AreaId ANALYSIS_POSITION_EDGE_SPLIT FatherObjectID = AreaId FatherObject2ID = EdgeIndex (0..) ANALYSIS_POSITION_EDGE_SPLIT_HOLE FatherObjectID = AreaId FatherObject2ID = 1000 * HoleIndex (0..) + EdgeIndex
